title: Make or Break Playcallers
itunes:title: Make or Break Playcallers
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including Michael Thomas' big new contract (7:18), Andrew Luck's setback at training camp (10:45), and the Redskins considering trading Trent Williams. (14:45) The heroes then discuss five new playcallers with make or break potential. (22:26)
